title: Grateful Dead - Dick's Picks 35 (Houseboat Tapes)
description:
Grateful Dead
Dick's Picks Vol. 35 - "The Houseboat Tapes"
Soundboard recordings from the summer of 1971

Ripped from HDCD CD directly to FLAC, 2005
Files have been stored on my external hard drive ever since

These are not their greatest performances by any means, but the whole set has a unique vibe to it. This is rock and roll!
